title: Reverse Fixer Upper - Week 12, Reviewed
description:
Week 12 left Spencer, Holly, and Ryan with many important questions, like:
Have Chip and Joanna ever found a corpse in a property?
Why do people agree to go to Iowa?
What do you with Utah at this point?
What's the meanest thing you can say about the Georgia offense?
How many people got convicted for that big biker shootout in Waco a while back?
What do Texas and Iowa State have in common?
